ENGLISH VERSION
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. PERMITTED USE
You are allowed to download, install, and use this modification/plugin ("Software")
for personal, non-commercial gameplay, single-player worlds, or non-commercial
Minecraft servers.

2. COMMERCIAL USE PROHIBITION
Commercial use of this Software is STRICTLY PROHIBITED without prior written
permission from the copyright holder. A server is considered "commercial" if it
generates any revenue, including but not limited to:
- Charging players for server access (Pay-to-Play).
- Selling in-game items, ranks, VIP status, or privileges (Pay-to-Win / Webstores).
- Accepting monetization, paid sponsorships, or mandatory donations tied to perks.
- Distributing this Software as a paid download or locked behind a paywall (e.g., Patreon-exclusive).

3. MODPACKS & DISTRIBUTION
You may include this Software in public or private modpacks, provided that the
modpack itself is entirely free to download and play, and does not violate Section 2.
You may not re-upload or redistribute the Software's binary (.jar) or source code
on other platforms without giving proper credit and linking back to the original source.

4. COMMERCIAL INQUIRIES
If you wish to use this Software on a commercial server, or for any revenue-generating
purposes, you MUST contact the author to negotiate a separate commercial license.
Contact Info: kevin@cloudxact.com or https://discord.gg/JyQPpVrhsk

